articles.title: Yiru Wang, Master
articles.contents:
Blog
This is a private blog site arranged for the ETC5523 course. I will be uploading two blogs on this site. In the first blog, I will give a brief overview of the Covid-19 virus in Russia. 
Professionalism
I am a first year MSc Business Analytics student from Monash University with an undergraduate degree from the Hebei University of Science and Technology. 
Private
In my spare time, I likes to read books or play sky. sky is a game I really like and recommend to all of you haha!
